00:06:07.190 --> 00:06:10.560 align:middle line:84%
The ability derives
from the fact

00:06:10.560 --> 00:06:13.130 align:middle line:84%
that we live in a
non-local world.

00:06:13.130 --> 00:06:16.910 align:middle line:84%
Now, non-locality, as I've
discovered at this conference,

00:06:16.910 --> 00:06:22.070 align:middle line:84%
has become a almost
metaphysical prospect.

00:06:22.070 --> 00:06:25.000 align:middle line:84%
But actually,
non-locality as it's

00:06:25.000 --> 00:06:27.590 align:middle line:84%
described today
in modern physics

00:06:27.590 --> 00:06:29.500 align:middle line:90%
has a very specific meaning.

00:06:29.500 --> 00:06:33.510 align:middle line:84%
It doesn't have any metaphysical
consequences at all,

00:06:33.510 --> 00:06:39.810 align:middle line:84%
but in fact is something that
Einstein observed in 1935.

00:06:39.810 --> 00:06:43.730 align:middle line:84%
Einstein said, quantum
mechanics predicts

00:06:43.730 --> 00:06:46.460 align:middle line:84%
that if photons go off
in opposite directions

00:06:46.460 --> 00:06:49.550 align:middle line:84%
at the speed of light
and you polarize

00:06:49.550 --> 00:06:52.480 align:middle line:84%
the photon on the left,
then the photon on the right

00:06:52.480 --> 00:06:55.470 align:middle line:90%
will change or notice that.

00:06:55.470 --> 00:06:57.780 align:middle line:84%
That's a prediction
of quantum mechanics.

00:06:57.780 --> 00:07:01.040 align:middle line:84%
And Einstein said that
could not be right.

00:07:01.040 --> 00:07:04.130 align:middle line:84%
So he talked about
a spooky action

00:07:04.130 --> 00:07:09.480 align:middle line:84%
at a distance that strongly
violated special relativity.

00:07:09.480 --> 00:07:12.660 align:middle line:84%
Relativity says that if things
are travelling away from each

00:07:12.660 --> 00:07:15.770 align:middle line:84%
other at the speed of light,
they cannot be connected.

00:07:15.770 --> 00:07:17.940 align:middle line:84%
In fact, that's the
essence of something

00:07:17.940 --> 00:07:20.370 align:middle line:90%
that can't be connected.

00:07:20.370 --> 00:07:25.180 align:middle line:84%
Well, Einstein was correct that
quantum mechanics does indeed

00:07:25.180 --> 00:07:28.290 align:middle line:84%
predict this spooky
connection at a distance.

00:07:28.290 --> 00:07:32.630 align:middle line:84%
But he was incorrect in that
starting in 1969 physicists

00:07:32.630 --> 00:07:35.890 align:middle line:84%
were able to demonstrate
that these photons,

00:07:35.890 --> 00:07:38.340 align:middle line:84%
born together,
these twin photons

00:07:38.340 --> 00:07:41.760 align:middle line:84%
remained connected
across the laboratory

00:07:41.760 --> 00:07:43.470 align:middle line:90%
and across the world.

00:07:43.470 --> 00:07:46.140 align:middle line:84%
Experiments started at
University of California

00:07:46.140 --> 00:07:50.080 align:middle line:84%
at Berkeley showing these
photons are connected.

00:07:50.080 --> 00:07:54.530 align:middle line:84%
And experiments have now been
done in France and Zurich.

00:07:54.530 --> 00:07:58.170 align:middle line:84%
So that you can have a
source of photons in Zurich.

00:07:58.170 --> 00:08:02.080 align:middle line:84%
One goes to Basel, the
other one goes to Geneva.

00:08:02.080 --> 00:08:05.900 align:middle line:84%
A physicist in Basel
turns his polarizer.

00:08:05.900 --> 00:08:08.900 align:middle line:84%
The photon in
Geneva notices that.

00:08:08.900 --> 00:08:10.980 align:middle line:84%
This is what we call a
non-local connection.

00:08:10.980 --> 00:08:14.970 align:middle line:84%
It's a connection that
transcends space and time.

00:08:14.970 --> 00:08:18.580 align:middle line:84%
It says that things can be
separated from one another

00:08:18.580 --> 00:08:20.370 align:middle line:90%
by physical distances.

00:08:20.370 --> 00:08:23.230 align:middle line:84%
And even though
they're separated,

00:08:23.230 --> 00:08:27.350 align:middle line:84%
they still are a part of
the same wave function.

00:08:27.350 --> 00:08:29.930 align:middle line:84%
They still are connected
to one another.

00:08:29.930 --> 00:08:32.549 align:middle line:84%
This is not a
metaphysical proposition,

00:08:32.549 --> 00:08:36.090 align:middle line:84%
although it's been
understood for many years.

00:08:36.090 --> 00:08:41.280 align:middle line:84%
J.S. Bell, who was the
discoverer of non-locality

00:08:41.280 --> 00:08:43.539 align:middle line:84%
in this current
formulation, said

00:08:43.539 --> 00:08:47.500 align:middle line:84%
that no description
of modern physics

00:08:47.500 --> 00:08:53.510 align:middle line:84%
compatible with
the quantum theory

00:08:53.510 --> 00:08:58.590 align:middle line:84%
that we have today, no modern
physical theory can be local

00:08:58.590 --> 00:09:01.080 align:middle line:90%
anymore.

00:09:01.080 --> 00:09:04.470 align:middle line:84%
Now this is actually
a very old idea.

00:09:04.470 --> 00:09:07.060 align:middle line:84%
In the earliest teachings
of the Buddha written

00:09:07.060 --> 00:09:11.800 align:middle line:84%
in Prajnaparamita 500 years
before Christ-- prajna

00:09:11.800 --> 00:09:15.510 align:middle line:84%
is wisdom and paramita
is the highest wisdom.

00:09:15.510 --> 00:09:20.420 align:middle line:84%
So Prajnaparamita, which is
the written teachings of Buddha

00:09:20.420 --> 00:09:21.870 align:middle line:90%
that have come down to us.

00:09:21.870 --> 00:09:23.450 align:middle line:90%
There are many versions.

00:09:23.450 --> 00:09:28.430 align:middle line:84%
But Prajnaparamita is very
holographic in that every page

00:09:28.430 --> 00:09:31.030 align:middle line:84%
says the same thing
in different words.

00:09:31.030 --> 00:09:36.180 align:middle line:84%
But it's what it's saying is so
unintuitive you have hundreds

00:09:36.180 --> 00:09:39.230 align:middle line:84%
and hundreds of pages to
eventually internalize

00:09:39.230 --> 00:09:40.850 align:middle line:90%
what they're saying.

00:09:40.850 --> 00:09:44.990 align:middle line:84%
And the basic ideas in the
earliest Buddhist teachings

00:09:44.990 --> 00:09:48.470 align:middle line:84%
is that separation
is an illusion.

00:09:48.470 --> 00:09:51.940 align:middle line:84%
That our consciousness
transcends space and time.

00:09:51.940 --> 00:09:54.800 align:middle line:84%
Our awareness is
able to experience

00:09:54.800 --> 00:09:58.720 align:middle line:84%
what's in the region where
we are, what's in the region

00:09:58.720 --> 00:10:02.000 align:middle line:84%
beyond where we are
physically, and indeed

00:10:02.000 --> 00:10:04.490 align:middle line:90%
into the future and the past.

00:10:04.490 --> 00:10:09.060 align:middle line:84%
And it's the idea that
the earliest Hindus had.

00:10:09.060 --> 00:10:12.050 align:middle line:90%
The Hindus said, all is brahman.

00:10:12.050 --> 00:10:17.690 align:middle line:84%
Brahman is the totality of
consciousness and materiality

00:10:17.690 --> 00:10:19.650 align:middle line:90%
in the universe.

00:10:19.650 --> 00:10:23.780 align:middle line:84%
Atman is our own
consciousness, our own soul,

00:10:23.780 --> 00:10:25.620 align:middle line:90%
our own awareness.

00:10:25.620 --> 00:10:28.880 align:middle line:84%
And the fundamental teaching
of the Hindu philosophy

00:10:28.880 --> 00:10:32.160 align:middle line:90%
is atman month equals brahman.

00:10:32.160 --> 00:10:37.620 align:middle line:84%
That is, our awareness is
one with all that there is.

00:10:37.620 --> 00:10:41.730 align:middle line:84%
The Buddhist teaching says
that separation is an illusion

00:10:41.730 --> 00:10:45.970 align:middle line:84%
so that the-- as you know,
the basic teaching of Buddhism

00:10:45.970 --> 00:10:47.440 align:middle line:90%
is compassion.

00:10:47.440 --> 00:10:50.210 align:middle line:84%
And the reason that
you're compassionate

00:10:50.210 --> 00:10:53.560 align:middle line:84%
is not particularly
to help other people

00:10:53.560 --> 00:10:55.560 align:middle line:90%
and be a good Boy Scout.

00:10:55.560 --> 00:10:58.580 align:middle line:84%
The reason you're compassionate
is that there is only one of us

00:10:58.580 --> 00:11:01.010 align:middle line:90%
here in consciousness.

00:11:01.010 --> 00:11:03.400 align:middle line:90%
That is, we are not bodies.

00:11:03.400 --> 00:11:05.110 align:middle line:90%
We each have a body.

00:11:05.110 --> 00:11:07.890 align:middle line:84%
The bodies give us an
illusion of separateness

00:11:07.890 --> 00:11:08.980 align:middle line:90%
without a doubt.

00:11:08.980 --> 00:11:11.235 align:middle line:84%
Bodies have all different
kinds of shapes.

00:11:11.235 --> 00:11:15.470 align:middle line:84%
They're sources of pleasure,
sources of discomfort.

00:11:15.470 --> 00:11:20.050 align:middle line:84%
We have bodies but we are not
the body that you see here.

00:11:20.050 --> 00:11:22.980 align:middle line:84%
What we are is
the awareness that

00:11:22.980 --> 00:11:25.700 align:middle line:84%
is able to transcend
space and time.

00:11:25.700 --> 00:11:28.810 align:middle line:84%
We can enjoy this
expanded awareness.

00:11:28.810 --> 00:11:33.770 align:middle line:84%
And what we notice when you go
shopping is it there's only one

00:11:33.770 --> 00:11:36.300 align:middle line:90%
of us here.

00:11:36.300 --> 00:11:40.970 align:middle line:84%
When you go to the grocery
store or go to Radio Shack

00:11:40.970 --> 00:11:45.670 align:middle line:84%
and the salesperson does
not treat you exactly

00:11:45.670 --> 00:11:47.520 align:middle line:84%
like you think you'd
like to be treated,

00:11:47.520 --> 00:11:50.055 align:middle line:84%
that does happen sometimes
in New York I've noticed.

00:11:50.055 --> 00:11:51.070 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

00:11:51.070 --> 00:11:54.130 align:middle line:84%
And what you notice is that
that person you're looking at

00:11:54.130 --> 00:11:57.470 align:middle line:84%
is in fact a
reflection of yourself.

00:11:57.470 --> 00:12:00.270 align:middle line:84%
That that encounter
is a holy encounter,

00:12:00.270 --> 00:12:03.060 align:middle line:84%
that you are seeing
yourself in the mirror

00:12:03.060 --> 00:12:06.160 align:middle line:84%
of the hard working
person that's struggling

00:12:06.160 --> 00:12:09.210 align:middle line:90%
to understand what you want.

00:12:09.210 --> 00:12:14.080 align:middle line:84%
So it's the idea that our ego
is a source of the separateness

00:12:14.080 --> 00:12:16.530 align:middle line:84%
and that we get very
attached to what

00:12:16.530 --> 00:12:19.782 align:middle line:84%
we're wearing, how our hair is
combed, who we think we are.

00:12:19.782 --> 00:12:22.450 align:middle line:84%
We all carry little
cards with us.

00:12:22.450 --> 00:12:25.960 align:middle line:84%
And what these cards actually
are, are story cards.

00:12:25.960 --> 00:12:27.480 align:middle line:90%
They're not business cards.

00:12:27.480 --> 00:12:30.701 align:middle line:84%
It's a story of who
we think we are today.

00:12:30.701 --> 00:12:32.450 align:middle line:84%
I look at my story
card, and it says today

00:12:32.450 --> 00:12:36.240 align:middle line:84%
and I'm a physicist here talking
at Saint John the Divine.

00:12:36.240 --> 00:12:39.110 align:middle line:84%
Tomorrow I may have a
totally different story.

00:12:39.110 --> 00:12:43.620 align:middle line:84%
And we get very attached
to these stories.

00:12:43.620 --> 00:12:48.080 align:middle line:84%
But what we discover
as we get increasingly

00:12:48.080 --> 00:12:51.170 align:middle line:84%
in touch with the
psychic part of ourselves

00:12:51.170 --> 00:12:55.700 align:middle line:84%
and that awareness can expand
through space and time,

00:12:55.700 --> 00:12:58.885 align:middle line:84%
these stories surprisingly
become less interesting.

00:12:58.885 --> 00:13:01.570 align:middle line:90%


00:13:01.570 --> 00:13:05.020 align:middle line:84%
What the spiritual
teachers tell us

00:13:05.020 --> 00:13:09.640 align:middle line:84%
is that we have the opportunity
for expanded awareness

00:13:09.640 --> 00:13:15.740 align:middle line:84%
to describe different modes
being, different ways of being

00:13:15.740 --> 00:13:17.330 align:middle line:90%
in the world.

00:13:17.330 --> 00:13:21.030 align:middle line:84%
And we have a choice as to
how we're going to do that.

00:13:21.030 --> 00:13:23.630 align:middle line:84%
In psychic abilities,
for example,

00:13:23.630 --> 00:13:27.270 align:middle line:84%
you have the opportunity
to inflow information

00:13:27.270 --> 00:13:29.470 align:middle line:90%
from a distant place.

00:13:29.470 --> 00:13:33.070 align:middle line:84%
This is called remote viewing,
where you can stand here

00:13:33.070 --> 00:13:35.740 align:middle line:84%
and psychically or
clairvoyantly experience

00:13:35.740 --> 00:13:39.100 align:middle line:84%
what's going on a
different distant place.

00:13:39.100 --> 00:13:44.230 align:middle line:84%
Similarly, you can outflow
your healing intention

00:13:44.230 --> 00:13:49.550 align:middle line:84%
to heal people who are sick or
suffering in a distant place.

00:13:49.550 --> 00:13:54.220 align:middle line:84%
Between the inflow in the
outflow is a quiet place

00:13:54.220 --> 00:13:58.360 align:middle line:84%
that you discover when you learn
to quiet the ongoing chatter.

00:13:58.360 --> 00:14:02.100 align:middle line:84%
And in that quiet place,
you have an opportunity

00:14:02.100 --> 00:14:06.510 align:middle line:84%
to reside in a loving space
that the mystics talk about

00:14:06.510 --> 00:14:08.940 align:middle line:90%
for millennia.

00:14:08.940 --> 00:14:13.990 align:middle line:84%
That quiet place has
many different names.

00:14:13.990 --> 00:14:17.420 align:middle line:84%
The Buddhists talk
about residing in love.

00:14:17.420 --> 00:14:20.940 align:middle line:84%
You have an opportunity
to experience

00:14:20.940 --> 00:14:23.540 align:middle line:84%
the oceanic
connection to all that

00:14:23.540 --> 00:14:27.310 align:middle line:84%
is, to all the forms
of consciousness

00:14:27.310 --> 00:14:28.550 align:middle line:90%
that there is in the world.

00:14:28.550 --> 00:14:31.160 align:middle line:84%
And you can experience
that directly

00:14:31.160 --> 00:14:34.540 align:middle line:90%
in this loving, quiet state.

00:14:34.540 --> 00:14:39.810 align:middle line:84%
And have an opportunity to be
out of time and out of space

00:14:39.810 --> 00:14:43.430 align:middle line:84%
and discover that you have
within you the love that you're

00:14:43.430 --> 00:14:45.260 align:middle line:90%
looking for.

00:14:45.260 --> 00:14:51.310 align:middle line:84%
Now this experience can be found
in a variety of different ways.

00:14:51.310 --> 00:14:53.500 align:middle line:84%
It could be found
through meditation,

00:14:53.500 --> 00:14:56.940 align:middle line:84%
which is the traditional
Hindu or Buddhist way.

00:14:56.940 --> 00:15:00.490 align:middle line:84%
It can be found through
centering prayer.

00:15:00.490 --> 00:15:03.045 align:middle line:84%
I had the privilege of sitting
with Thomas Keating, who

00:15:03.045 --> 00:15:07.350 align:middle line:84%
is a great Catholic mystic
who teaches centering prayer.

00:15:07.350 --> 00:15:09.320 align:middle line:84%
You can choose a
word or a phrase

00:15:09.320 --> 00:15:13.170 align:middle line:84%
or an idea to focus your
mind upon and achieve

00:15:13.170 --> 00:15:16.900 align:middle line:84%
the same quietness that
the Buddhists talk about.

00:15:16.900 --> 00:15:22.210 align:middle line:84%
There's also drug experiences
that we heard about yesterday.

00:15:22.210 --> 00:15:25.940 align:middle line:84%
And there are many different
paths you can follow.

00:15:25.940 --> 00:15:29.230 align:middle line:84%
I've had an opportunity
to follow many of those.

00:15:29.230 --> 00:15:33.270 align:middle line:84%
I had the privilege of sitting
with Ram Dass a number of years

00:15:33.270 --> 00:15:38.120 align:middle line:84%
ago just after he was
recovering from his stroke.

00:15:38.120 --> 00:15:40.070 align:middle line:84%
And one of the things--
he had a meeting

00:15:40.070 --> 00:15:44.240 align:middle line:84%
with people on the West Coast
who think about these things

00:15:44.240 --> 00:15:44.740 align:middle line:90%
and teach.

00:15:44.740 --> 00:15:50.080 align:middle line:84%
And he said, it's very important
that those of you who finally

00:15:50.080 --> 00:15:53.830 align:middle line:84%
cracked open your
analytical mind

00:15:53.830 --> 00:15:57.950 align:middle line:84%
and had an experience of God
or a transcendent experience,

00:15:57.950 --> 00:16:00.990 align:middle line:84%
if you've had that
experience through drugs,

00:16:00.990 --> 00:16:04.260 align:middle line:84%
it's a lie to pretend that
you had the experience

00:16:04.260 --> 00:16:06.870 align:middle line:90%
from a lifetime of meditation.

00:16:06.870 --> 00:16:08.750 align:middle line:84%
So one of the
things that he said

00:16:08.750 --> 00:16:11.320 align:middle line:84%
is that it's time
the teachers who've

00:16:11.320 --> 00:16:16.100 align:middle line:84%
had the benefit of a variety
of different mind opening

00:16:16.100 --> 00:16:18.680 align:middle line:84%
chemicals, it's time
to tell the truth

00:16:18.680 --> 00:16:21.330 align:middle line:84%
and describe that these
chemicals can give you

00:16:21.330 --> 00:16:25.090 align:middle line:84%
an experience of
quieting your mind,

00:16:25.090 --> 00:16:29.660 align:middle line:84%
residing in a loving state,
discovering that there is more

00:16:29.660 --> 00:16:32.430 align:middle line:84%
to you than is on
your business card

00:16:32.430 --> 00:16:39.170 align:middle line:84%
and that the awareness you have
transcends your physical body.

00:16:39.170 --> 00:16:42.540 align:middle line:84%
So there are many paths
to this awareness.

00:16:42.540 --> 00:16:48.440 align:middle line:84%
And this has been taught
by mystics throughout ages.

00:16:48.440 --> 00:16:51.820 align:middle line:84%
That is, all the mystics
are teaching the same thing.

00:16:51.820 --> 00:16:55.100 align:middle line:84%
The great surprise as
I became interested

00:16:55.100 --> 00:16:59.090 align:middle line:84%
in this, that is the
teaching of oneness

00:16:59.090 --> 00:17:01.450 align:middle line:84%
is the universal
teaching-- a mystical

00:17:01.450 --> 00:17:04.260 align:middle line:84%
is a person who doesn't
ask you to believe a thing.

00:17:04.260 --> 00:17:06.060 align:middle line:90%
That's very important.

00:17:06.060 --> 00:17:09.440 align:middle line:90%
There's the mystic Sufis.

00:17:09.440 --> 00:17:11.670 align:middle line:84%
So you have the direct
experience of God

00:17:11.670 --> 00:17:12.470 align:middle line:90%
that's available.

00:17:12.470 --> 00:17:16.490 align:middle line:84%
The Kabbalistic Jews say that
if you will study the Kabbalah

00:17:16.490 --> 00:17:21.960 align:middle line:84%
you can go directly to Ein
Sof and be one with God.

00:17:21.960 --> 00:17:26.730 align:middle line:84%
In the Christian tradition,
the Gnostic Christians

00:17:26.730 --> 00:17:31.400 align:middle line:84%
said that we are still receiving
the direct transmission

00:17:31.400 --> 00:17:32.140 align:middle line:90%
of Jesus.

00:17:32.140 --> 00:17:36.650 align:middle line:84%
Jesus' physical body is
gone, but we, 100 years

00:17:36.650 --> 00:17:39.890 align:middle line:84%
after the death of
Christ, do not need

00:17:39.890 --> 00:17:43.250 align:middle line:90%
bishops or priests or deacons.

00:17:43.250 --> 00:17:45.400 align:middle line:84%
Jesus is still
transmitting to us

00:17:45.400 --> 00:17:49.460 align:middle line:84%
and we are still experiencing
the transmission.

00:17:49.460 --> 00:17:56.140 align:middle line:84%
So it's quite interesting
that the mystic Christians

00:17:56.140 --> 00:17:58.580 align:middle line:84%
or like Gnostics
or the Kabbalistic

00:17:58.580 --> 00:18:03.350 align:middle line:84%
Jews or the Buddhists or
the Hindus, they all agree.

00:18:03.350 --> 00:18:06.290 align:middle line:84%
There's no disagreement
about the fact

00:18:06.290 --> 00:18:09.960 align:middle line:84%
that it's possible
to quiet your mind,

00:18:09.960 --> 00:18:14.290 align:middle line:84%
reside in love as a
place to live your life.

00:18:14.290 --> 00:18:17.385 align:middle line:84%
This is not about
boyfriends and girlfriends.

00:18:17.385 --> 00:18:21.270 align:middle line:84%
It's actually beyond
relationships.

00:18:21.270 --> 00:18:22.690 align:middle line:90%
I know it's hard to believe.

00:18:22.690 --> 00:18:28.320 align:middle line:84%
But it's possible to reside in
a loving space through your day.

00:18:28.320 --> 00:18:31.970 align:middle line:84%
And after you've discovered
that the love you're looking for

00:18:31.970 --> 00:18:34.890 align:middle line:84%
is within you, it
is quite likely

00:18:34.890 --> 00:18:38.080 align:middle line:90%
going to change your life.

00:18:38.080 --> 00:18:39.680 align:middle line:90%
In fact, I had this experience.

00:18:39.680 --> 00:18:42.130 align:middle line:90%
I was an aerospace engineer.

00:18:42.130 --> 00:18:45.840 align:middle line:84%
And I had done that for many
years and I was well paid

00:18:45.840 --> 00:18:48.280 align:middle line:84%
and what I was doing
was quite interesting.

00:18:48.280 --> 00:18:51.430 align:middle line:84%
And as I went through
this process putting

00:18:51.430 --> 00:18:56.230 align:middle line:84%
lasers on spacecraft
simply became boring.

00:18:56.230 --> 00:18:57.600 align:middle line:90%
Became absurd.

00:18:57.600 --> 00:19:01.040 align:middle line:84%
It no longer seemed
like an appropriate way

00:19:01.040 --> 00:19:04.890 align:middle line:84%
to spend my time since I had the
feeling that other people could

00:19:04.890 --> 00:19:05.930 align:middle line:90%
do that.

00:19:05.930 --> 00:19:07.520 align:middle line:84%
And there are fewer
people who were

00:19:07.520 --> 00:19:11.510 align:middle line:84%
going to stand up
and say that you have

00:19:11.510 --> 00:19:15.330 align:middle line:84%
the love within you that
you're looking for in a way

00:19:15.330 --> 00:19:19.320 align:middle line:84%
to try and encourage
people to look inside

00:19:19.320 --> 00:19:23.200 align:middle line:84%
through some kind of procedure,
whether it's meditation

00:19:23.200 --> 00:19:27.410 align:middle line:84%
or prayer or some other
approach to discover

00:19:27.410 --> 00:19:30.420 align:middle line:84%
that what all of the
mystics have been saying

00:19:30.420 --> 00:19:34.390 align:middle line:84%
is something that's
available to us today.

00:19:34.390 --> 00:19:37.800 align:middle line:84%
Now this experience
of oceanic connection,

00:19:37.800 --> 00:19:42.210 align:middle line:84%
the opportunity to reside
in a kind of loving syrup,

00:19:42.210 --> 00:19:45.655 align:middle line:84%
is an idea this common
to all traditions.

00:19:45.655 --> 00:19:48.350 align:middle line:90%


00:19:48.350 --> 00:19:52.750 align:middle line:84%
It could even be the
equivalent to saying,

00:19:52.750 --> 00:19:56.225 align:middle line:84%
we are experiencing love
or we are experiencing God.

00:19:56.225 --> 00:19:58.750 align:middle line:90%


00:19:58.750 --> 00:20:03.030 align:middle line:84%
In my upbringing as
a Jewish physicist,

00:20:03.030 --> 00:20:06.670 align:middle line:84%
I always would hear, in
the Christian theology

00:20:06.670 --> 00:20:09.570 align:middle line:84%
on Sunday morning they
would say, God is love.

00:20:09.570 --> 00:20:11.580 align:middle line:84%
And nobody ever
unpacked that for me.

00:20:11.580 --> 00:20:14.306 align:middle line:84%
I thought that's something
that ministers say just

00:20:14.306 --> 00:20:15.430 align:middle line:90%
to annoy the non-believers.

00:20:15.430 --> 00:20:18.690 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

00:20:18.690 --> 00:20:21.070 align:middle line:90%


00:20:21.070 --> 00:20:24.270 align:middle line:84%
So it's quite interesting
is that what you have is

00:20:24.270 --> 00:20:26.330 align:middle line:90%
a different spiritual writings.

00:20:26.330 --> 00:20:28.335 align:middle line:84%
You have the Koran
and the New Testament

00:20:28.335 --> 00:20:33.180 align:middle line:84%
and the Old Testament
and the Bhagavad Gita

00:20:33.180 --> 00:20:36.200 align:middle line:90%
and the writings of Buddha.

00:20:36.200 --> 00:20:38.400 align:middle line:84%
They are all trying
to remind you

00:20:38.400 --> 00:20:43.600 align:middle line:84%
that you are already connected
to a kind of psychic internet.

00:20:43.600 --> 00:20:46.100 align:middle line:84%
You have that
connection within you.

00:20:46.100 --> 00:20:50.800 align:middle line:84%
We all have this ability
to reside in love.

00:20:50.800 --> 00:20:55.340 align:middle line:84%
But each of the different
organized religion

00:20:55.340 --> 00:20:59.260 align:middle line:84%
has different software
available to make

00:20:59.260 --> 00:21:03.160 align:middle line:84%
you aware of the
connection between yourself

00:21:03.160 --> 00:21:06.780 align:middle line:84%
and the psychic internet that
you're already connected to.

00:21:06.780 --> 00:21:09.610 align:middle line:84%
The thing that's very amazing is
that all the religious strife,

00:21:09.610 --> 00:21:12.590 align:middle line:84%
all the holy wars,
are over software.

00:21:12.590 --> 00:21:16.220 align:middle line:84%
It's not over religious
differences at all.

00:21:16.220 --> 00:21:18.850 align:middle line:84%
It's over simply
what process are

00:21:18.850 --> 00:21:21.750 align:middle line:84%
you going to use
to awaken yourself,

00:21:21.750 --> 00:21:26.710 align:middle line:84%
to wake up to the fact that you
have this connection already

00:21:26.710 --> 00:21:29.070 align:middle line:90%
hardwired in you.

00:21:29.070 --> 00:21:31.560 align:middle line:84%
The Harvard philosopher
says that God

00:21:31.560 --> 00:21:34.480 align:middle line:84%
is a testable
hypothesis, that we're

00:21:34.480 --> 00:21:40.960 align:middle line:84%
hardwired for God, that we have
an innate desire and capability

00:21:40.960 --> 00:21:43.630 align:middle line:84%
to have this
religious experience.

00:21:43.630 --> 00:21:48.060 align:middle line:84%
Herbert Benson is the one who
talked about the relaxation

00:21:48.060 --> 00:21:48.990 align:middle line:90%
response.

00:21:48.990 --> 00:21:55.710 align:middle line:84%
Relaxation response is Harvard
code for quieting your mind

00:21:55.710 --> 00:21:58.430 align:middle line:84%
and having a
transcendent experience.

00:21:58.430 --> 00:22:01.195 align:middle line:84%
God and Harvard have always
had a hard time together.

00:22:01.195 --> 00:22:02.250 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

00:22:02.250 --> 00:22:10.160 align:middle line:84%
So they talk about relaxation
response, but in recent years

00:22:10.160 --> 00:22:12.260 align:middle line:84%
Herbert Benson is
talking about the fact

00:22:12.260 --> 00:22:14.360 align:middle line:90%
that we are hardwired for God.

00:22:14.360 --> 00:22:18.960 align:middle line:84%
We have an innate desire
to have this experience.

00:22:18.960 --> 00:22:23.210 align:middle line:84%
And the experience is something
that is part of a path.

00:22:23.210 --> 00:22:24.870 align:middle line:90%
It shows up.

00:22:24.870 --> 00:22:30.530 align:middle line:84%
The Hindu teacher Patanjali,
who was 100 years after Buddha--

00:22:30.530 --> 00:22:36.370 align:middle line:84%
Patanjali was a great teacher
and grammarian and logician.

00:22:36.370 --> 00:22:38.980 align:middle line:90%
This is 400 years before Christ.

00:22:38.980 --> 00:22:45.060 align:middle line:84%
Patanjali is leading us in
his book "How to Know God."

00:22:45.060 --> 00:22:48.230 align:middle line:84%
You can tell that he's a
great teacher because his book

00:22:48.230 --> 00:22:53.210 align:middle line:84%
written 2,400 years ago is still
available at Barnes & Noble's.

00:22:53.210 --> 00:22:56.960 align:middle line:84%
That's one of the
great enduring classic.

00:22:56.960 --> 00:22:59.820 align:middle line:84%
And Patanjali is
principally telling us

00:22:59.820 --> 00:23:03.280 align:middle line:84%
how to quiet our minds
to experience God.

00:23:03.280 --> 00:23:05.260 align:middle line:84%
And he says, along
the way you will

00:23:05.260 --> 00:23:07.730 align:middle line:84%
have certain
interesting experiences.

00:23:07.730 --> 00:23:11.680 align:middle line:84%
You will discover that you
can look into the distance,

00:23:11.680 --> 00:23:15.560 align:middle line:84%
you can look into the future,
you can heal the sick,

00:23:15.560 --> 00:23:17.550 align:middle line:90%
you can diagnose illnesses.

00:23:17.550 --> 00:23:19.880 align:middle line:84%
And these abilities
will come to you.

00:23:19.880 --> 00:23:24.610 align:middle line:84%
And he describes
in great detail how

00:23:24.610 --> 00:23:27.130 align:middle line:84%
you are able to do that and
the things that interfere

00:23:27.130 --> 00:23:29.000 align:middle line:90%
with your ability to do that.

00:23:29.000 --> 00:23:32.040 align:middle line:84%
He talks about the
fact that your memory

00:23:32.040 --> 00:23:36.340 align:middle line:84%
and your imagination and your
analysis and your guessing

00:23:36.340 --> 00:23:39.500 align:middle line:84%
interfere with your
innate capacity

00:23:39.500 --> 00:23:43.360 align:middle line:84%
to experience what's
hidden from view.

00:23:43.360 --> 00:23:46.310 align:middle line:84%
He says, but it's very
important to notice

00:23:46.310 --> 00:23:50.780 align:middle line:84%
that as these abilities
begin to appear,

00:23:50.780 --> 00:23:53.990 align:middle line:84%
the good news is that you are
learning to quiet your mind.

00:23:53.990 --> 00:23:59.450 align:middle line:84%
You're learning to stop and
stifle the ongoing chatter.

00:23:59.450 --> 00:24:01.130 align:middle line:84%
However, it's very
important not to get

00:24:01.130 --> 00:24:03.580 align:middle line:90%
attached to this ability.

00:24:03.580 --> 00:24:07.670 align:middle line:84%
These abilities are
just more phenomena.

00:24:07.670 --> 00:24:09.750 align:middle line:84%
And what Patanjali
is trying to do

00:24:09.750 --> 00:24:12.740 align:middle line:84%
is lead us to an experience
of transcendence.

00:24:12.740 --> 00:24:15.690 align:middle line:84%
He's trying to lead
us to experience

00:24:15.690 --> 00:24:18.250 align:middle line:90%
outside of ourselves.

00:24:18.250 --> 00:24:22.860 align:middle line:84%
Now many people get attached
to the idea, my goodness,

00:24:22.860 --> 00:24:26.190 align:middle line:90%
I can find parking places.

00:24:26.190 --> 00:24:30.640 align:middle line:84%
I've learned to quiet my
mind and do a procedure that

00:24:30.640 --> 00:24:35.400 align:middle line:84%
allows me to use my psychic
ability to forecast the stock

00:24:35.400 --> 00:24:36.691 align:middle line:90%
market.

00:24:36.691 --> 00:24:38.940 align:middle line:84%
Now one of the interesting
things that you've probably

00:24:38.940 --> 00:24:43.750 align:middle line:84%
heard is that it's like as if
God won't let you use your ESP

00:24:43.750 --> 00:24:45.540 align:middle line:90%
to enrich yourself.

00:24:45.540 --> 00:24:46.365 align:middle line:90%
It's not true.

00:24:46.365 --> 00:24:52.032 align:middle line:90%


